{"tid":2083758,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"用手杖86歲長者，旺角下車即被拘捕","createTime":"2020-06-29T03:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T00:52:17.000Z","uid":5195,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe193dff11fe34376e5de8020e1793fa36ae380","tid":2083758,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:20:58.000Z","msg":"唔怕國安法，只怕亂執法，<br />\n                有感而發！<br />\n作日我們四個朋友，相約在旺角彌敦道，紅茶咖啡室，四點九下午茶，到四點左右，其中一個朋友（86歲)要用手杖，來電，話在登打士街前下車，因警察封路未能通過，幾分鐘後我們打電話給他，打算叫他落油麻地地鐵站坐地鐵回美孚方向，誰知他只回應已被警察截停問話之後電話就一值關機，幾經多方查找，最後得知已被帶到紅磡警署，<br />\n                以上我只講出事件過情，實際情況我不敢猜測，各位自已判斷，誰對誰錯。<br />\n<br />\n好消息：我朋友已經回家了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1516279288669918/posts/2408967676067737?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1516279288669918%2Fposts%2F2408967676067737%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8XjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=1e532023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1516279288669918/posts/2408967676067737?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5597d6214032c8e99456cad26a5b7836f63b19bd","tid":2083758,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"癡鳩線"},{"pid":"6ed028c52ea4030793124e2d37af9755c7b6f236","tid":2083758,"uid":114487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEpj5kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEpj5kb.jpg&h=d66f7ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2KDBrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2KDBrX.jpg&h=a5c2a855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4w0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cz4w0k.jpg&h=82cb5faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n決定前聽一聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"htt